column2: "I've been hearing people talk about how impressive your chops are."
"But I like to say the proof of the pudding is in the eating, if you get my drift."
"So what do you say? Are you up for a time attack? You know, a race to achieve a goal faster than others."
"Of course, I expect you to clear my test with a max rating on top of finishing before you're out of time."
"Set a record, claim your bounty. What do you got to lose?"
